{"tid":1758238,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【修例風波】理大今再派員進入校園 林大輝冀警盡快解封","createTime":"2019-11-27T02:34:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T02:36:21.000Z","uid":56881,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d2a7a17b8b0dab88efeffb0148271208fbe9dfde","tid":1758238,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:34:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/i5tZ3qIuo8gO3xgpcXoIHg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20191127a091651.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fi5tZ3qIuo8gO3xgpcXoIHg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20191127a091651.jpg&h=15de34b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紅十字會人員進入理大。<br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】理工大學被圍封至今第11日，校董會主席林大輝表示，理大今日最派員進入校園，但今日會是最後一日，相信留守校園的人已十分少，而且不是激進示威者，無能力進行破壞，即使大學職員清場都不會攻擊他們。<br />\n<br />\n林大輝出席電台節目時表示，每次進入校園都會感到傷心和痛心，因衛生條件愈來愈差，水浸嚴重，希望警方盡快解封現場，交回理大管理。<br />\n<br />\n林大輝指，區議會建行派大敗，相信示威者不會再攻擊理大，希望警方同意18歲以上的人士離開理大時都是先登記，讓留守者釋疑離開，社會人士會監察警方做法。<br />\n<br />\n林大輝又說，理大停課已接近兩星期，影響深遠，不少科研成果可能毀於一旦，希望校園盡快解封。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E4%BB%8A%E5%86%8D%E6%B4%BE%E5%93%A1%E9%80%B2%E5%85%A5%E6%A0%A1%E5%9C%92-%E6%9E%97%E5%A4%A7%E8%BC%9D%E5%86%80%E8%AD%A6%E7%9B%A1%E5%BF%AB%E8%A7%A3%E5%B0%81-011200600.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2-%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E5%2593%25A1%25E9%2580%25B2%25E5%2585%25A5%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E5%259C%2592-%25E6%259E%2597%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25BC%259D%25E5%2586%2580%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%259B%25A1%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E5%25B0%2581-011200600.html&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRL0p1Vm5vkyQgjvFoLOApLI%3D&h=e58b99c8\" target=\"_blank\">https